        "p1": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Three years of cracked heels and thick callouses. I'd tried everything — drugstore foot creams, a $40 callus shaver, a $90 pedicure that lasted four days. <strong>Nothing softened the dryness.</strong> By March my heels were splitting open and catching on bedsheets.</p>"
